o Mercier and Dan Sperber (book){{BACKSLASH}}n{{BACKSLASH}}nAtrophy of Deep Thinking  {{BACKSLASH}}n{{BACKSLASH}}{{DQUOTE}}The Shallows: What the Internet Is Doing to Our Brains{{BACKSLASH}}{{DQUOTE}} by Nicholas Carr (book)  {{BACKSLASH}}n{{BACKSLASH}}{{DQUOTE}}Deep Work{{BACKSLASH}}{{DQUOTE}} by Cal Newport (book){{BACKSLASH}}n{{BACKSLASH}}nDecline in Information Literacy  {{BACKSLASH}}nStanford History Education Group{{QUOTE}}s studies on civic online reasoning  {{BACKSLASH}}n{{BACKSLASH}}{{DQUOTE}}Web Literacy for Student Fact-Checkers{{BACKSLASH}}{{DQUOTE}} by Mike Caulfield (open textbook){{BACKSLASH}}n{{BACKSLASH}}nExploitation of Cognitive Vulnerabilities  {{BACKSLASH}}n{{BACKSLASH}}'});
